 o elements of the genre. This month's theme will be: Thriller. Dennis Leha
 ne's Shutter Island \, the basis for the blockbuster motion picture direct
 ed by Martin Scorsese and starring Leonardo DiCaprio\, is a gripping and a
 tmospheric psychological thriller where nothing is quite what it seems. U.
 S. Marshal Teddy \\n\\nMore info: https://chipublib.bibliocommons.com/even
